1
00:00:22,850 --> 00:00:29,850
♪Our tangled destiny
has trapped my heart in this life♪

2
00:00:30,020 --> 00:00:36,060
♪Will I see you again in the next life♪

3
00:00:36,550 --> 00:00:43,500
♪Keep a piece of peach blossom
to remember the past and say goodbye♪

4
00:00:43,830 --> 00:00:49,920
♪But I still miss you
with tears in my eyes♪

5
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:57,250
♪Dig a hole, plant a tree, but the leaves
and flowers remind me of our past♪

6
00:00:57,480 --> 00:01:03,710
♪Sow the seeds of love,
but they bloom on the wrong path♪

7
00:01:04,340 --> 00:01:11,060
♪Move on, let go,
forget everything about you♪

8
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:18,220
♪Flowers fall on the road
where I fell in love with you♪

9
00:01:33,020 --> 00:01:37,660
=Stolen Love=

10
00:01:37,860 --> 00:01:40,700
=Episode 31=

11
00:01:57,390 --> 00:01:59,510
Yi, when we set off,

12
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:01,240
she'll have become the lady in charge.

13
00:02:01,780 --> 00:02:03,040
What are you worried about?

14
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:06,400
We can set off

15
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,760
after Brother gets the scroll.

16
00:02:10,130 --> 00:02:11,640
But the Crown Prince said

17
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:13,240
Father ordered us to escort

18
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:14,960
the supplies out of the capital today.

19
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,440
Crown Prince?

20
00:02:18,940 --> 00:02:20,360
I'm afraid he'll take action tonight.

21
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:25,400
Liuyun, I made a promise,

22
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,400
and I'll do it.

23
00:02:28,650 --> 00:02:29,870
However, I'm really worried that

24
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,240
Brother can't deal with it alone.

25
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:32,800
When this is over,

26
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:34,240
I'll come back immediately.

27
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:38,400
It was Prince Su
who asked me to take you away.

28
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:41,160
They've turned against each other.

29
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:44,200
If there's no evidence,
and we're not involved,

30
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:45,560
he'll have a way out.

31
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:50,680
Your Highness.

32
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:03,840
Take it.

33
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:06,680
Xiao Chuyi, our marriage is canceled.

34
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,320
You can leave.

35
00:03:14,880 --> 00:03:15,720
Go!

36
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:17,960
Go!

37
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:24,800
Your Highness,

38
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,680
why did you let the Prince Consort go?

39
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:31,640
I thought Lu Yunxi
only wanted money and fame.

40
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:32,480
However,

41
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:34,280
she's waited for seven years

42
00:03:34,920 --> 00:03:36,600
only to avenge the Xiaos.

43
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,280
Such a wonderful woman

44
00:03:38,640 --> 00:03:40,960
deserves the best man in the world.

45
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:49,640
These explosives

46
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:52,800
can ruin the entire ancestral hall.

47
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:58,480
My Lady, have you made up your mind?

48
00:04:00,760 --> 00:04:01,600
Brother.

49
00:04:02,160 --> 00:04:03,360
If you ignite the explosives,

50
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:05,160
you'll die here too.

51
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:06,400
Brother.

52
00:04:07,480 --> 00:04:09,560
If Father sees the scroll,

53
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:12,480
I'll be a traitor to the nation

54
00:04:12,480 --> 00:04:13,440
and live in hell!

55
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:16,480
Now that all of you
can go to hell with me,

56
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,520
I'd like a quick death.

57
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:24,480
My Lady, if you put the scroll back,

58
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:28,040
I can pretend that nothing has happened,

59
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:31,640
and all of you can enjoy money and power

60
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:33,200
and serve the country.

61
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:35,040
My Lady,

62
00:04:35,840 --> 00:04:38,880
I promise you I'll secure your position.

63
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,320
It's been seven years.

64
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:44,040
You must be tired.

65
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:48,520
My Lady, please put it back!

66
00:04:48,520 --> 00:04:50,480
Please have mercy!

67
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:52,600
My Lady, don't kill us!

68
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:54,600
Please agree!

69
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:57,760
My Lady, please agree!

70
00:04:57,760 --> 00:05:00,040
My Lady!

71
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:03,200
My Lady, please agree!

72
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:06,080
My Lady, please!

73
00:05:06,080 --> 00:05:08,120
My Lady, please agree!

74
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:31,840
Take Che away tonight.

75
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,400
Find Xiao Chuyi

76
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:36,040
and Princess Liuyun
after the Mid-Autumn Festival.

77
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:01,440
Go!

78
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,440
Run!

79
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:25,520
Run!

80
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:41,760
Xiao Chuyi.

81
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:43,640
I'm the Crown Prince!

82
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,520
Crown Prince?

83
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:50,520
You're the Crown Prince of Wujiang.

84
00:07:01,400 --> 00:07:02,440
Stop them!

85
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:03,960
They have the scroll.

86
00:07:03,960 --> 00:07:05,360
They can't leave!

87
00:07:07,700 --> 00:07:09,420
(Zhou Family Ancestral Hall)

88
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:10,280
Chuyi!

89
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:11,760
Give me the scroll.

90
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,320
Brother,

91
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,960
I'll never risk Yun's life

92
00:07:14,960 --> 00:07:16,040
for your revitalization

93
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:18,920
or my revenge.

94
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,440
When she's safe,

95
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:22,280
I'll give it to you.

96
00:07:40,340 --> 00:07:42,620
(Xiao's Mansion)

97
00:07:54,130 --> 00:07:59,310
♪Flowers fall on the riverbank♪

98
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:03,280
I'll take you and Che away tonight

99
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:05,040
and find a safe place.

100
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:09,160
Yun,

101
00:08:09,880 --> 00:08:11,240
you've done enough.

102
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:13,840
Please let me take care of the rest.

103
00:08:13,850 --> 00:08:15,640
♪Still waiting for you♪

104
00:08:16,220 --> 00:08:18,980
♪When will my lover come back♪

105
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:19,840
No.

106
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:23,320
You're the Prince Consort.

107
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:25,440
Che and I can leave on our own.

108
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:28,600
Her Highness and I
have canceled the marriage.

109
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:30,960
What?

110
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:33,560
We're just friends.

111
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,320
I agreed to marry her

112
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:37,600
only to help her
avoid the royal marriage.

113
00:08:41,210 --> 00:08:43,090
♪How time flies♪

114
00:08:45,680 --> 00:08:46,520
Yun.

115
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,390
I know you still love me.

116
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:50,780
♪Miss you day and night♪

117
00:08:50,800 --> 00:08:51,640
This time,

118
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:54,080
I'll never let you go.

119
00:08:56,560 --> 00:08:57,400
Chuyi.

120
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,760
I've never forgotten you

121
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,800
or Mother.

122
00:09:04,500 --> 00:09:08,520
♪And have stayed true to each other,
forgetting the passing of time♪

123
00:09:08,800 --> 00:09:10,530
♪If there's another life♪

124
00:09:10,530 --> 00:09:14,420
♪We'll be birds of a feather♪

125
00:09:15,460 --> 00:09:17,200
♪If we fall in love again♪

126
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:21,240
Mom!

127
00:09:23,680 --> 00:09:24,920
Mom!

128
00:09:25,500 --> 00:09:27,920
- Che.
- You're right on time.

129
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:31,920
Yun,

130
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:33,360
I'll prepare for our departure.

131
00:09:33,640 --> 00:09:34,520
I'll be right back.

132
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:38,120
Che,

133
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:39,560
it's time to test your martial arts.

134
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:41,080
Protect your mother.

135
00:09:43,760 --> 00:09:45,800
No problem. Don't worry, Master.

136
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:54,920
Chuyi! Che...

137
00:10:01,160 --> 00:10:03,880
Che and I will be waiting for you.

138
00:10:05,160 --> 00:10:06,000
Life is long.

139
00:10:06,520 --> 00:10:07,800
Tell me everything when I'm back.

140
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:12,320
Go.

141
00:10:15,520 --> 00:10:16,360
Go.

142
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:22,680
Cuixi,

143
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:24,240
help us get changed.

144
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:27,920
Yunxi.

145
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:41,160
Yunxi,

146
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:42,800
please don't go, okay?

147
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,360
You're the only family I have.

148
00:10:44,560 --> 00:10:45,400
Yanyu,

149
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:47,440
I wanted to spend
the rest of my life with you.

150
00:10:48,930 --> 00:10:50,080
Even when Chuyi came back,

151
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:51,720
I didn't change my mind.

152
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:54,080
However, I can't believe

153
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:55,680
you want to kill him.

154
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:02,120
I'm afraid you advised His Highness

155
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:04,320
to bury the explosives
in advance, right?

156
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:06,520
I had a thorough plan,

157
00:11:06,520 --> 00:11:07,380
but...

158
00:11:07,380 --> 00:11:09,200
but I've never wanted to hurt you.

159
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:14,680
I just don't want Prince Su
to get the scroll

160
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:16,360
because in that case,

161
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:18,320
you'd leave me.

162
00:11:30,340 --> 00:11:32,220
(Divorce Paper)

163
00:11:36,040 --> 00:11:37,320
Are you divorcing me?

164
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:39,920
Yanyu.

165
00:11:42,040 --> 00:11:43,680
Stop making more mistakes.

166
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:45,640
The past seven years were just a dream.

167
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:47,200
Be a loyal servant.

168
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:50,200
You'll meet someone
who really loves and cares about you.

169
00:11:52,400 --> 00:11:53,360
A dream?

170
00:12:12,800 --> 00:12:14,600
I wish I could kill him!

171
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:19,640
He should've died seven years ago!

172
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:22,200
If it wasn't for him,

173
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:25,320
I'd never work with the Crown Prince!

174
00:12:28,800 --> 00:12:30,040
I've tried every means

175
00:12:30,800 --> 00:12:32,840
to get closer to you.

176
00:12:34,680 --> 00:12:36,240
Now that Lady Yun is dead,

177
00:12:37,120 --> 00:12:39,000
no one can stop us anymore.

178
00:12:42,600 --> 00:12:43,480
Zhou Yanyu!

179
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:45,560
You're so cruel!

180
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:46,680
Lady Yun...

181
00:12:48,120 --> 00:12:50,520
Lady Yun was pregnant with your baby!

182
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:51,920
No.

183
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:54,440
That was not my child!

184
00:12:55,520 --> 00:12:56,520
Che is my child.

185
00:13:00,760 --> 00:13:01,600
Zhou Yanyu.

186
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:04,560
As your ex-wife,

187
00:13:05,400 --> 00:13:08,400
I won't tell others what you did.

188
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:12,880
Don't go too far.

189
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:17,160
Yunxi!

190
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:42,520
Your master is here.

191
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:56,920
I couldn't make everyone
in the capital envy you.

192
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:58,680
You've also given up

193
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:00,720
your position, haven't you?

194
00:14:37,680 --> 00:14:38,560
Che!

195
00:14:38,880 --> 00:14:39,880
Che, where does it hurt?

196
00:14:48,640 --> 00:14:49,480
This...

197
00:14:52,640 --> 00:14:54,360
I think the poison is from the palace.

198
00:14:56,880 --> 00:14:58,360
Che! Che!

199
00:15:16,210 --> 00:15:18,170
♪My cries♪

200
00:15:18,290 --> 00:15:19,890
♪And sighs♪

201
00:15:20,330 --> 00:15:23,170
♪Are buried in the snow♪

202
00:15:24,170 --> 00:15:25,890
♪Horses run♪

203
00:15:26,050 --> 00:15:27,570
♪Into my dreams♪

204
00:15:28,010 --> 00:15:31,290
♪And I see you again♪

205
00:15:31,850 --> 00:15:33,570
♪You left♪

206
00:15:33,690 --> 00:15:35,410
♪Broke my heart♪

207
00:15:35,570 --> 00:15:39,450
♪Wish you could hold me in your arms♪

208
00:15:40,050 --> 00:15:42,290
♪Even your name♪

209
00:15:42,490 --> 00:15:46,770
♪Is a forbidden word♪

210
00:15:47,850 --> 00:15:50,890
♪I've traveled a thousand miles♪

211
00:15:50,890 --> 00:15:55,130
♪Only to keep the moon in sight♪

212
00:15:55,130 --> 00:15:58,570
♪For it once shone upon your face♪

213
00:15:59,330 --> 00:16:02,530
♪When you looked at me in the eye♪

214
00:16:03,290 --> 00:16:06,290
♪I've said goodbye a thousand times♪

215
00:16:06,290 --> 00:16:10,170
♪Only to call your name again♪

216
00:16:10,570 --> 00:16:14,250
♪For it's the only thing♪

217
00:16:14,530 --> 00:16:18,250
♪I'll never forget♪

