00:16:37,290 --> 00:16:41,250
♪Only to call your name again♪

224
00:16:41,570 --> 00:16:44,930
♪For it's the only thing♪

225
00:16:45,450 --> 00:16:49,250
♪I'll never forget♪

226
00:16:53,130 --> 00:16:56,490
♪Till the day that I die♪
